ors-find-a-shared-beat</link><description>两个量子振荡器的同步揭示了仅在它们的相关性中编码的集体节奏。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-oscillators-find-a-shared-beat2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 12:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/quantum-oscillators-find-a-shared-beat</guid></item><item><title>新的驾驶模型以类人般的准确度预测瞬间避免碰撞</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-driving-model-predicts-split-second-crash-avoidance-with-humanlike-accuracy</link><description>代尔夫特理工大学的科学家与 Waymo 合作， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-driving-model-predicts-split-second-crash-avoidance-with-humanlike-accuracy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 12:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-driving-model-predicts-split-second-crash-avoidance-with-humanlike-accuracy</guid></item><item><title>光激活化合物通过自身的防御酶来对抗抗生素耐药性细菌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/light-activated-compound-kills-antibiotic-resistant-bacteria-by-turning-its-own-defense-enzyme-against-it</link><description>由于多年来抗生素的过度使用和滥用，抗生素耐药性正在成为一场日益严重的危机。当抗生素消灭敏感细菌但留下耐药细菌繁殖并进一步传播耐药性时，问题就会加剧。人们正在不断寻找对抗耐药细菌的新疗法，现在研究人员可能已经找到了一种成功治疗至少一种耐药细菌的方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/light-activated-compound-kills-antibiotic-resistant-bacteria-by-turning-its-own-defense-enzyme-against-it2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 11:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/light-activated-compound-kills-antibiotic-resistant-bacteria-by-turning-its-own-defense-enzyme-against-it</guid></item><item><title>钚化合物解锁罕见的拓扑量子行为，具有潜在的核科学应用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/plutonium-compound-unlocks-rare-topological-quantum-behavior-with-potential-nuclear-science-applications</link><description>钚是元素周期表中最复杂的元素之一。钚由加州大学伯克利分校的科学家于 1940 年首次合成并分离出来，人们对钚的研究已超过 80 年。它通常与它在核安全中的作用联系在一起，但它对核电也至关重要，它是在反应堆中生产的，可以作为燃料回收。尽管钚很重要，但它的一些最基本的行为仍然是个谜。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/plutonium-compound-unlocks-rare-topological-quantum-behavior-with-potential-nuclear-science-applications2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/plutonium-compound-unlocks-rare-topological-quantum-behavior-with-potential-nuclear-science-applications</guid></item></channel></rss>